{"tid":1256514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"借醉揸護士胸部再拳打對方眉心僅判囚4個月，青年拒戒酒官斥毫無悔意但可保釋等候上訴。","createTime":"2019-06-25T05:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:45:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"40f6d432970d8d39e49d4af67cd4c407a370f986","tid":1256514,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"男子與女友吵架後買醉昏倒，被送往天水圍醫院急症室救治，期間他疑借醉揸護士胸部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又拳打對方眉心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，受審後被裁定非禮和普通襲擊兩罪罪成，今(25日)在屯門法院判刑，裁判官斥被告毫無悔意，借酒行兇，判入獄4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但准保釋等候上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190625/bkn-20190625111314410-0625_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190625%2Fbkn-20190625111314410-0625_00822_001.html&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443gESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=d9f72de2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190625/bkn-20190625111314410-0625_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ba16aa6e8bfdbccca35c84f2b3762d5b15258e9","tid":1256514,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"辯方求情稱，26歲被告陳文迪已感到後悔，他自17歲開始飲酒，隨着年紀增長，生活壓力也愈來愈大，所以他開始藉酒精逃避，經常飲到爛醉。他雖然拒絕感化官的戒酒建議，但承諾會減少飲酒量至每天不多於6罐。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190625/photo/bkn-20190625111314410-0625_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190625112739\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190625%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190625111314410-0625_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190625112739&h=493db097&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n裁判官斥被告因爛醉如泥而送院，至案發一刻已接近全面清醒，應知道自己做了甚麼，但他在護士施行急救時襲擊對方，勢打擊醫護人員對工作的信心。裁判官指法庭近日亦曾處理同類案件，故必須判具阻嚇力刑罰，否則同類事件會一再發生。"},{"pid":"656ddba4cf9e20e87819cc87651904ba89a6895c","tid":1256514,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdb9e1d1cbf150cc44f2b0e523753a1265d8bef","tid":1256514,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"飲咁多都咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec1c77ae414c1309198a1417e9c99a5eef24ac3","tid":1256514,"uid":220438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"最憎呢啲死酒鬼 唔飲又要學人飲 飲大左發神經 見到呢啲人一腳踢佢春袋等佢即時醒曬"},{"pid":"508853a5dd22ca610c539951a4ac917a2d14fcad","tid":1256514,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"68ae39d9be661f922d3c0a652f17b57b8c5b46f9","tid":1256514,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"但承諾會減少飲酒量至每天不多於6罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49d5fe184ba9c8f4c367261c29f56b3698526e7","tid":1256514,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68ae39d9be661f922d3c0a652f17b57b8c5b46f9","tid":1256514,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"但承諾會減少飲酒量至每天不多於6罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbef245b184feb112eb3c01f73c78e5b3e2724f0","tid":1256514,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"一日6罐又真係唔會醉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr